 <div class="title" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">AVERAGE PHENOTYPES</div>
 <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Taking the expectation of equation 
  <a rid="evo12635-disp-0001" ref-type="disp-formula" href="#evo12635-disp-0001">(1)</a>, we have 
