      <span class="mo">*</span>
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div> is the covariance between the maternal effect and the maternal phenotype after selection. Subsequently, we assess how 
  <div id="nlm-math-282" class="math">
   <div class="msub">
    <span class="mi">C</span>
    <div class="mrow">
     <div class="msub">
      <span class="mi">m</span>
