          <span class="mo">−</span>
          <span class="mi">τ</span>
          <span class="mo">−</span>
          <span class="mn">1</span>
         </div>
        </div>
        <span class="mo">+</span>
        <div class="msub">
         <span class="mi">C</span>
         <div class="mrow">
          <div class="msubsup">
           <span class="mi">m</span>
           <div class="mrow">
            <span class="mi">t</span>
            <span class="mo">−</span>
            <span class="mn">1</span>
           </div>
           <span class="mo">*</span>
          </div>
          <div class="msubsup">
           <span class="mi">z</span>
           <div class="mrow">
            <span class="mi">t</span>
            <span class="mo">−</span>
            <span class="mn">2</span>
           </div>
           <span class="mo">*</span>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
        <span class="mo">+</span>
        <div class="msub">
         <div accent="true" class="mover">
          <span class="mi">m</span>
          <span class="mo">¯</span>
         </div>
         <span class="mi">t</span>
        </div>
        <div class="msubsup">
         <div accent="true" class="mover">
          <span class="mi">z</span>
          <span class="mo">¯</span>
         </div>
         <div class="mrow">
          <span class="mi">t</span>
          <span class="mo">−</span>
          <span class="mn">2</span>
         </div>
         <span class="mo">*</span>
        </div>
        <span class="mo">,</span>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>where we assume that breeding values for 
  <span class="italic">a</span>, 
  <span class="italic">b</span>, and 
  <span class="italic">m</span> are transmitted without bias from parents to offspring (implying weak selection and random mating; Falconer 
  <a rid="evo12635-bib-0015" ref-type="ref" href="#evo12635-bib-0015">1985</a>; Hadfield 
  <a rid="evo12635-bib-0022" ref-type="ref" href="#evo12635-bib-0022">2012</a>), so that 
  <div id="nlm-math-289" class="math">
   <div class="mrow">
    <div class="msubsup">
     <div accent="true" class="mover">
      <span class="mi">a</span>
      <span class="mo">¯</span>
     </div>
     <div class="mrow">
      <span class="mi">t</span>
      <span class="mo">−</span>
      <span class="mn">1</span>
     </div>
     <span class="mo">*</span>
    </div>
    <span class="mo">≈</span>
    <div class="msub">
     <div accent="true" class="mover">
      <span class="mi">a</span>
      <span class="mo">¯</span>
     </div>
     <span class="mi">t</span>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>, 
  <div id="nlm-math-290" class="math">
   <div class="mrow">
    <div class="msubsup">
     <div accent="true" class="mover">
      <span class="mi">b</span>
      <span class="mo">¯</span>
     </div>
     <div class="mrow">
      <span class="mi">t</span>
      <span class="mo">−</span>
      <span class="mn">1</span>
     </div>
     <span class="mo">*</span>
    </div>
    <span class="mo">≈</span>
    <div class="msub">
     <div accent="true" class="mover">
      <span class="mi">b</span>
      <span class="mo">¯</span>
     </div>
     <span class="mi">t</span>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>, and 
  <div id="nlm-math-291" class="math">
   <div class="mrow">
    <div class="msubsup">
     <div accent="true" class="mover">
      <span class="mi">m</span>
      <span class="mo">¯</span>
     </div>
     <div class="mrow">
      <span class="mi">t</span>
      <span class="mo">−</span>
      <span class="mn">1</span>
     </div>
     <span class="mo">*</span>
    </div>
    <span class="mo">≈</span>
    <div class="msub">
     <div accent="true" class="mover">
      <span class="mi">m</span>
      <span class="mo">¯</span>
     </div>
     <span class="mi">t</span>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>. Moreover, note that neither 
  <div id="nlm-math-292" class="math">
   <div class="msub">
    <span class="mi">C</span>
    <div class="mrow">
     <div class="msubsup">
      <span class="mi">m</span>
      <div class="mrow">
       <span class="mi">t</span>
